[[e4modularity_prereq">
== Prerequisites
	
		The following assumes that you have already a basic understanding of how Android applications are created. See the
		https://www.vogella.com/tutorials/Android/article.html[Android Tutorial]
		for details. Also the following description assume that you know the basis of the Android build system based on
		Gradle. See
		https://www.vogella.com/tutorials/AndroidBuild/article.html[Building Android applications with Gradle Tutorial]
		for an introduction.
	
	
		For more information about Gradle see the
		https://www.vogella.com/tutorials/Gradle/article.html[Gradle Tutorial]
		.

	

